The paper deals with the impact of cyber attacks on a Cyber Physical System (CPS) which consists of cyber components for computation and communication, and physical components such as sensors and actuators for process control. The paper specifically focuses on a water distribution system and investigates the behavior of the system in response to attacks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Other likely categories include cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
